Form description
Dear Respondents, I am a Masters Student at Front Lane Campus of NCBA&E & this questionnaire is designed to elicit your responses on my research. The questionnaire does not ask for your identity or that of your organizations and your honest reply will not harm you in any way. We plan to gather like 300 responses and cumulative results will be shown to readers hence the privacy of each respondent is well maintained and assured. No one can sort out which was your individual response and you are secure. The purpose of this survey is only academic. The survey will take less than 10 minutes to complete.
I Thank you for your honest response and cooperation.
